{"tid":364969,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【維基變身759？】林偉駿：長江後浪推前浪 拭目以待！","createTime":"2017-08-18T23:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T11:27:13.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22a11dcf65226ed5ad44e6eb83f9ccfcac21d457","tid":364969,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T23:20:18.000Z","msg":"港視(1137)HKTVmall大增實體店，曾承認大肆開店是錯誤的759阿信屋(母企為CEC國際、759)老闆林偉駿表示，如果HKTVmall分店是開在住宅區，而該區又具消費潛力，開實體店屬合理。他指出，只要「計得掂數」，港視要開實體店一定無難度，問題在於開店後經營策略。<br />\n<br />\n他指不評論行家做法，不過「長江後浪推前浪」，港視主席王維基又是生意人，作為香港人，見到有人在香港投資屬開心事，會拭目以待未來HKTVmall的概念店。<br />\n<br />\n至於去年暫時關閉的759網上業務，林偉駿則指因運輸等成本問題，仍未打算重開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170818/large/1503064967_2a48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170818%2Flarge%2F1503064967_2a48.jpg&h=eb3bbd31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57099310&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57099310%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170818&d=jKMfaIENg%2FsepRZOusneR%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=a78b747e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57099310%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170818&h=17161ee7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57099310&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170818</a>"},{"pid":"6d363ecf4657f7a78c7ff2eac062b06c03c0cf7c","tid":364969,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T11:27:13.000Z","msg":"顧掂自己先喇，759就執就執咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}